QuestData.Title: A Tentative Pact
QuestData.Description: Very well, $n. Your people kept their end of the bargain.$B$BTell Dumont that we'll honor the deal.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return to Lieutenant Dumont in Amberpine Lodge.
QuestData.RewardText: Excellent news, $n. With the locals' help we'll have the logistical support we need to outmaneuver the Horde in this region.$B$BI have further tasks for you if you're interested.
